    "client_msg_id": "A85644C5-D304-4DE2-9B45-166AF20731D7",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Main takeaway from me: there's a lot more to the research going on in Web3 that's really not apparent until you get pretty deep into it. As people in the FoC world I think many of us can empathise there.\n\nAnyone who wants to try and build bridges between our community and related research communities in the Web3 space let me know, always up for a chat!",
